com.lg.ar_utilities

Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lg.ar_utilities.Entity

  • public class Entity
extends Object
    This is the structure to store information of an AR Entity. Either LBS (Billboards or 3d models) or IBS (3d models).
    Author:
    Dimitrios Ververidis for the Multimedia Group (http://mklab.iti.gr).
